Help BarbarianRaces:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Most barbarians in Ansalon are human nomads, Kagonesti elves, or ogres.  
Almost all other races produce occasional barbarians, with the exception of
the gnomes of Mt. Nevermind.  Even kender raised in wild regions have been
known to become fierce wilderness warriors.
